<title>UK: SOCCER-RONALDO VOTED BEST PLAYER IN MAGAZINE POLL.</title>
<headline>SOCCER-RONALDO VOTED BEST PLAYER IN MAGAZINE POLL.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-12-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Barcelona striker Ronaldo eclipsed Newcastle's Alan Shearer to win World Soccer magazine's player of the year title, the publication said on Friday.</p>
<p>George Weah of AC Milan came third in the readers' poll.</p>
<p>Berti Vogts was voted best manager after steering Germany to European championship success.</p>
<p>He received nearly three times as many votes as Alex Ferguson, who guided Manchester United to a second English league and cup double.</p>
<p>Top 10 players:</p>
<p>1. Ronaldo (Barcelona and Brazil)</p>
<p>2. Alan Shearer (Newcastle and England)</p>
<p>3. George Weah (AC Milan and Liberia)</p>
<p>4. Matthias Sammer (Borussia Dortmund and Germany)</p>
<p>5. Juergen Klinsmann (Bayern Munich and Germany)</p>
<p>6. Gabriel Batistuta (Fiorentina and Argentina)</p>
<p>7. Eric Cantona (Manchester United)</p>
<p>8. Nwankwo Kanu (Internazionale and Nigeria)</p>
<p>9. Jari Litmanen (Ajax and Finland)</p>
<p>10. Gianluca Vialli (Chelsea and Italy).</p>
